abbott (Amanuensis for BusyBodies on Twisted TAC) is an XMPP bot based on
Twisted and Wokkel.

CONFIGURATION:
 1. Create a new XMPP account user@domain.com
 2. Edit abbott.tac and replace abbott@ransford.org with user@domain.com
 3. Put user@domain.com's password in a file 'password.txt' in this directory

USAGE: twistd -ny abbott.tac
  -or- twistd -y abbott.tac     # daemonize
